General.Name: Nord Insuretech Group AB
General.Description: Nord Insuretech Group AB (publ) operates a digital platform that allows users and partners to sell various insurance products in Norway. Its platform operates as an intermediary that delivers digital and white-label solutions to consumers and businesses. The company was formerly known as Hudya AB (publ) and changed its name to Nord Insuretech Group AB (publ) in January 2021. Nord Insuretech Group AB (publ) was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
